Package: situas
Type: Package
Title: Client for the SITUAS API - Italian Territorial Codes and Classifications
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Giampaolo",
    family = "Montaletti",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "giampaolo.montaletti@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-5327-1122")
  )
Description: Provides functions to download and cache territorial codes and
    classifications from the SITUAS API (https://situas.istat.it), maintained
    by ISTAT (Italian National Institute of Statistics). Enables reclassification
    of old territorial codes to new ones and batch detection/cleaning of
    territorial codes in datasets.
